{"tid":140052,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"各位巴打點睇Jeep Grand Cherokee?","createTime":"2017-03-02T02:20:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-06T21:09:51.000Z","uid":27919,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bdde56f54d89fb4cd9b3b65e3ac8467bbd8445a2","tid":140052,"uid":27919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T02:20:11.000Z","msg":"我想問下連登有冇Jeep grand cherokee嘅車主或者曾經揸過呢架車嘅巴打？其他巴打對呢架車有咩評價？<br />\n<br />\n是咁的，細佬我準備年中換車。我夢想係想換WRX sti, 但我上網Google 過同上YouTube 睇過，佢車內籠嘅engine 聲好大聲。我住緊悉尼，間唔中會揸長途車去下其他洲玩，如果成8，9個鐘都嘈住會好辛苦，舒適度黎講始終SUV會好啲。所以最終都係要對現實低頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 夢想就繼續發下夢就算啦。<br />\n<br />\n最近睇中左Jeep嘅Grand Cherokee，想聽下各位巴打點睇呢架車？呢架車會唔會經常壞？內籠嘅皮梳化cum唔cum?電子野易唔易壞？希望有經驗嘅巴打幫手俾下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/02/101946_dc971d73d3f46616e6137d653ac2b40c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F02%2F101946_dc971d73d3f46616e6137d653ac2b40c.jpg&h=9825c898&s={SIZE}\" />網上圖片<br />\n<br />\nYouTube 嘅介紹短片<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/peShriFyFSI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpeShriFyFSI&d=PwwdVKvQMhnOdjdmHJS5OTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=66fd3b08\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/peShriFyFSI</a>"},{"pid":"7ddc2fcbc65f85b17040fd0c78057cd09231f4ce","tid":140052,"uid":31809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T02:23:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zaYFLb8WMGM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzaYFLb8WMGM&d=PwwdVKvQMhnOdjdmHJS5OTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=ff988053\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zaYFLb8WMGM</a><br />\n睇完你就唔會買"},{"pid":"5cd08b755c7ec0e24114c82dcad8740205f1af06","tid"