ota 4runner, tundra, honda pilot 唔好 aftermarket 嘢又多"},{"pid":"0f89f3257584c5d96b0a7a4edf4516ab76c75c05","tid":140052,"uid":15186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:46:00.000Z","msg":"btw 唔清楚澳州咩玩法<br />\n去外州 點解唔租車仲方便<br />\n日日揸大車食油 <br />\n揸細車啲用小嘅油夠你租車玩 又唔洗煩係外州壞車"},{"pid":"1baeae7a57db653c972af18208dfa974ea3df4b7","tid":140052,"uid":10790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T07:04:48.000Z","msg":"睇過之前有個外國佬買左部grand Cher整極都整唔好就拍片dup爛部車"},{"pid":"bd28bb070db7048df0169de04a9acc9907eb8f33","tid":140052,"uid":6959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T07:29:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a49e67a7fbc869534590ff1e09fe48ad93855c9b","tid":140052,"uid":27919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T11:10:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>btw 唔清楚澳州咩玩法<br />\n去外州 點解唔租車仲方便<br />\n日日揸大車食油 <br />\n揸細車啲用小嘅油夠你租車玩 又唔洗煩係外州壞車</blockquote><br />\n揸自己車點都舒服過租車嘅<br />\n而且平時番工放工塞車都好舒服咁坐入邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"863bb2420db0e8cdfd4501f8e9a5eb1e32f32cb7","tid":140052,"uid":27919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T11:15:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>美國車真係得啖笑<br />\n唔好講咁多 去dealer 坐上去試下 坐得舒唔舒服 再test drive<br />\n美國車係美國都冇resale value. 入面做工冇特別 <br />\n講真實買架toyota 4runner, tundra, honda pilot 唔好 aftermarket 嘢又多</blockquote><br />\n本身都對美國車冇乜好感<br />\n但係睇左網上對呢架車嘅評價整體上都ok<br />\n所以先對佢有興趣<br />\n<br />\nTest drive 就一定要架啦，始終架車都要跟我好多年，想之前聽聽大家嘅睇法姐<br />\n<br />\n另外問下<br />\n全新2017 Overland ～AUD$76000 drive away 算唔算好唔值？"},{"pid":"03143694cfcc0bc1385775f474a4049369ed5116","tid":140052,"uid":15186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T23:35:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>美國車真係得啖笑<br />\n唔好講咁多 去dealer 坐上去試下 坐得舒唔舒服 再test drive<br />\n美國車係美國都冇resale value. 入面做工冇特別 <br />\n講真實買架toyota 4runner, tundra, honda pilot 唔好 aftermarket 嘢又多</blockquote><br />\n本身都對美國車冇乜好感<br />\n但係睇左網上對呢架車嘅評價整體上都ok<br />\n所以先對佢有興趣<br />\n<br />\nTest drive 就一定要架啦，始終架車都要跟我好多年，想之前聽聽大家嘅睇法姐<br />\n<br />\n另外問下<br />\n全新2017 Overland ～AUD$76000 drive away 算唔算好唔值？</blockquote><br />\n咁架咩 美國我諗加埋dealer sale 40k out the door"},{"pid":"93c9a1e759e361b31e22da6ed0fee6df6aac7f6a","tid":140052,"uid":8963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T00:03:39.000Z","msg":"掃把唔定得WRX 同 sti, 點解唔睇下forester？<br />\nToyota Prado 依類四驅都唔錯<br />\n美國車真係分分鐘整多過揸，之前有個鬼佬買左架jeep 就係整多過揸仲要拍片笑尻架車，條片 YouTube search  I bought a Lemon 就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03a6e55749b419944dca173d69a770ca2198469a","tid":140052,"uid":58791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T05:37:55.000Z","msg":"買JEEP更係買呢款黎改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://pic.yasn.com/MMS/Pic/2012-05-04/57a000fb-007e-4c96-ad8e-52190f2592ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.yasn.com%2FMMS%2FPic%2F2012-05-04%2F57a000fb-007e-4c96-ad8e-52190f2592ad.jpg&h=7b6d95a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"84c777bb08de76c63554f26ae82eb0579e432390","tid":140052,"uid":27919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T02:52:19.000Z","msg":"巴打咁Range Rover Evoque呢架又如何？<br />\n上網睇d人話land Rover 會成日漏engine 油<br />\n而且interior 電子野又好易壞。<br />\n唔知新款嗰啲會唔會都係咁呢？<br />\n評價麻麻但又見到好多人買喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ls0fCh1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLs0fCh1.jpg&h=4ed564cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a9067a9dd10280299d02a74107e4b7fc33d75d2","tid":140052,"uid":27919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T02:56:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打咁Range Rover Evoque呢架又如何？<br />\n上網睇d人話land Rover 會成日漏engine 油<br />\n而且interior 電子野又好易壞。<br />\n唔知新款嗰啲會唔會都係咁呢？<br />\n評價麻麻但又見到好多人買喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif